A floral amalgam, and a storm gruezok.<br>
Amalgam is a flower, gruezok is a bear.<br>
As with the trees, don't be fooled by the same model; there is another type of flower and another type of bear that are pure melee that summon, and that will HURT your pet ( and you ) a lot. <p>Forever sharp is the sword of Justice.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=leyringores>LeyrinGores</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#333333>(12/18/02 8:13:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=24.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Plane of Storms (AKA: AA Heaven)</span><hr size=1> Tryed this yesterday and to my surprise.... Trees are not rooted. LOL.<br>
