The mobs are druids, so when they get low life they heal themselves.  It's no crazy regen (Cazel they're not, thank you Lord), just a heal they cast on themselves.  With regard to malosini, the only reason I cast that is the first few times I hunted here I had fbot resisted on occasion.  I'm not one to enjoy 500 mana being wasted, so I hit 'em with malo.<br>
